Q.)Problem Statement 2: Spring Boot REST API 
Develop a Spring Boot REST API for Student Registration Management. 
The REST API should: 
Provide an endpoint to register a new student (Student ID, Name, Course, Email, 
Marks). 
Provide an endpoint to view all registered students. 
Provide an endpoint to search a student by Student ID. 
Provide an endpoint to update student details. 
Provide an endpoint to delete a student record by Student ID. 
Return appropriate HTTP status codes for all operations. 
Use Controller and Service layers, and store data using in-memory collection or 
database. 
Test all REST endpoints using Postman 
�
