Student Registration Management - Spring Boot REST API 
�
� Project Description 
A complete Spring Boot REST API for Student Registration Management with CRUD operations, 
proper HTTP status codes, Service layer, and in-memory storage. 
�
�
️ Technology Stack 
Component 
Technology 
Framework Spring Boot 4.0.1 
API Type 
REST API 
Web Layer Spring MVC (@RestController) 
Storage 
In-Memory (ArrayList) 
Service Layer @Service 
Build Tool 
Maven 
Java Version 17 
Testing Tool Postman 
✨ Features Implemented 
✅ Register new student (POST) - Student ID, Name, Course, Email, Marks 
✅ View all students (GET) - Returns list of all students 
✅ Search student by ID (GET) - Find specific student 
✅ Update student details (PUT) - Modify existing student 
✅ Delete student (DELETE) - Remove student record 
✅ Proper HTTP status codes - 200, 201, 404, 409, etc. 
✅ Service layer - Separation of business logic 
✅ ResponseEntity - Professional REST responses 
