� How to Run 
Prerequisites 
• JDK 17 or higher 
• Maven 3.6+ 
• Postman (for testing) 
Steps 
1. Extract/Clone the project 
2. Navigate to project directory 
bash 
cd StudentRegistrationAPI 
3. Build the project 
bash 
mvn clean install 
4. Run the application 
bash 
mvn spring-boot:run 
5. Application starts on: http://localhost:8080 
6. Base URL for API: http://localhost:8080/students 
