� HTTP Status Codes Used 
Status Code 
200 OK 
201 Created 
When Used 
GET (found), PUT (updated), DELETE (deleted) 
Description 
Success 
Resource created POST (new student registered) 
204 No Content Success but no data GET all students (empty list) 
404 Not Found Resource not found GET/PUT/DELETE (student doesn't exist) 
409 Conflict 
Duplicate resource POST (student ID already exists) 
�
� Complete Postman Test Sequence 
Test Scenario 1: Happy Path 
1. ✅ POST /students - Register student 1️01️ → 2️01️ Created 
2. ✅ POST /students - Register student 1️02️ → 2️01️ Created 
3. ✅ GET /students - View all → 2️00 OK (shows 2️ students) 
4. ✅ GET /students/101 - Search → 2️00 OK (found) 
5. ✅ PUT /students/101 - Update → 2️00 OK (updated) 
6. ✅ DELETE /students/102 - Delete → 2️00 OK (deleted) 
7. ✅ GET /students - View all → 2️00 OK (shows 1️ student) 
Test Scenario 2: Error Handling 
1. ❌ POST /students - Duplicate ID 1️01️ → 409 Conflict 
2. ❌ GET /students/999 - Not found → 404 Not Found 
3. ❌ PUT /students/999 - Update non-existent → 404 Not Found 
4. ❌ DELETE /students/999 - Delete non-existent → 404 Not Found 
5. ✅ GET /students - Empty list → 2️04 No Content (if all deleted) 
